Kxh7 17. Rxh6+ Kg7 18. a3 $3 $16) 15. Nd4 $1 Bxc3+ 16. Qxc3 Kxh7 17. Nxc6 bxc6
18. Qxc5 $14 {and White has the better bishop. There are doubtless a lot more
