the stereotyped structure with Black having 4v3 on the Kingside, and White
having 3v2 on the Queenside.} c5 4. Ngf3 cxd4 5. exd5 Qxd5 6. Bc4 Qd8 {The
minor differences between the queen retreats can get a bit much sometimes.} ({
